ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend the course to another student since anyone coming out of the course knows what OO programming is all about. A student from this course would write programs that are way more efficient in terms of memory and programs that are bug free.
Yes. U can learn a lot of stuff from this course. But if this course can be more deepgoing, it would be better.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I have learnt most of the stuff. I hope that we can skip some very basic knowledge about c++ and say sth more about template, inheritance, std, etc. After all, students are expected to know the basics of programming.
